        {
            "id": "https://cazzola.click/telos.html",
            "url": "https://cazzola.click/telos.html",
            "title": "Telos",
            "summary": "<h5>Details:</h5>\n<h6></h6>\n<h6></h6>\n<ul>\n<li>A 3D platforming game.</li>\n<li>8 week development (20h/week) with a team of 5 programmers, 4 level designers and 5 artists. Game project 4 at The Game Assembly.</li>\n<li>Made in TGE, the school's in-house C++ game engine.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>My contibutions:</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>The collision system which is based on ray vs box interection.</li>\n<li>The intro and outro scripted events.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"post__iframe\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WDW5AWl-FtY?start=9&amp;mute=1\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\n",
            "content_html": "<h5>Details:</h5>\n<h6></h6>\n<h6></h6>\n<ul>\n<li>A 3D platforming game.</li>\n<li>8 week development (20h/week) with a team of 5 programmers, 4 level designers and 5 artists. Game project 4 at The Game Assembly.</li>\n<li>Made in TGE, the school's in-house C++ game engine.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>My contibutions:</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>The collision system which is based on ray vs box interection.</li>\n<li>The intro and outro scripted events.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"post__iframe\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WDW5AWl-FtY?start=9&amp;mute=1\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\n\n<h5>Ray vs box collision system:</h5>\n<p>During the project I implemented the collision system which was based on <a href=\"https://youtu.be/8JJ-4JgR7Dg\">javidx9 Youtube video</a>. </p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  style=\"outline: 3px solid rgba(var(--color-primary-rgb), 0.55)  !important;\" src=\"https://cazzola.click/media/posts/2/telos-collision.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"248\"></figure>",
